markets.title: Will the FDV ratio of Avalanche:Solana be above 0.20 before Jan 1, 2026?
markets.rules_primary: If the FDV ratio of Avalanche to Solana is above 0.20 at any point before Jan 1, 2026, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The ratio is calculated as the fully diluted valuation of the first token divided by the fully diluted valuation of the second token, both in USD as reported by CoinGecko. The market monitors continuously from issuance through the target date. If either token's FDV becomes unavailable or shows as null/zero on CoinGecko, the market resolves based on the last valid ratio before data became unavailable.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the FDV ratio definitively crosses the threshold.
